column2: When the Persians were upon us, the proud Ionians and Aegeans banded together to resist them. The time has come once again for the bonds to brotherhood to be reforged in the face of new dangers. A new league of independent city states on the coast of Asia will allow us to better repel barbarians and the Hellenistic Kings!
We will gain claims over all of the coastal provinces of the #Y Asia#! region.
We will gain claims the provinces of #Y Achaea#! and #Y Arcadia#!.
